   equilibrium results with the rainout results, with an eye to
   understanding the near-infrared spectrum of Gliese 229B, as well as the
   new ``L dwarfs{''} with T-eff's above similar to 1500 K. We address the
   issue of the formation and composition of clouds in the cool atmospheres
